<div class="account-wall-static">

  <div id="intro">
    <h1 style="font-weight:500;">Rush Application</h1>
    <h3 style="color:#b5b5b5;">Application Complete</h3>
    <br />

    <p class="rushapp-body">
      You have successfully submitted your online application. You will receive a confirmation email in your inbox shortly at <%="#{@rush_application.email}" %>

      Please print out a copy of the application. You can access it by clicking <%=link_to "here", print_rush_application_path(@rush_application, confirmation: @rushee.password_digest), :method => :post%>

      Additionally, please bring the following application materials to your professional interview at your scheduled time.

      Candidate Application
      Cover letter
      Resume
      Schedule of current coursework
      Unofficial transcript with your name from Bear Facts
      Recent photo of yourself (this will not be returned)

      Thank you for rushing Alpha Kappa Psi. We wish you the best of luck with the rush process. Click <%= link_to "here", root_url %> to return to the website.
